    question: 'How should I prepare for installation day?',
    answer:
      'Clear furniture and personal items from the rooms being worked on. Remove wall decorations and fragile items near the work area. Ensure the space is accessible and keep pets and children away from the installation zone. Our team handles the rest, including removing old flooring if that is part of your project. We provide detailed preparation instructions during your free estimate appointment.',
